Template: vmelilo-installer/noroot
Type: error
_Description: No root partition found
 No partition is mounted as your new root partition.
 You must mount a root partition first.

Template: vmelilo-installer/writeconf
Type: text
_Description: Creating vmelilo configuration...

Template: vmelilo-installer/conferr
Type: error
_Description: Failed to create vmelilo configuration
 The creation of the vmelilo configuration file failed.
 .
 Please check the system log or the output on the third console (tty3).
 .
 Warning: Your system may be unbootable!

Template: vmelilo-installer/writeboot
Type: text
_Description: Installing vmelilo into bootstrap partition...

Template: vmelilo-installer/booterr
Type: error
_Description: Failed to install bootloader
 The installation of the vmelilo boot loader failed.
 .
 Please check the system log or the output on the third console (tty3).
 .
 Warning: Your system may be unbootable!

Template: vmelilo-installer/success
Type: note
_Description: Successfully installed vmelilo
 The vmelilo boot loader was successfully installed.
 .
 The system is now ready to boot the new Debian GNU/Linux system.

